videos.headline: Texas drives down the field for the first score of game
videos.description: Texas wide receiver Lil'Jordan Humphrey makes a tough grab to set up 1-yard QB sneak for Sam Ehlinger.

videos.headline: Longhorns running wild with 29-yard TD
videos.description: Texas running back Keaontay Ingram runs for a 29-yard score to put the Longhorns up by 2 touchdowns.

videos.headline: Texas' Humphrey catches his second TD of the first half
videos.description: Texas wide receiver Lil'Jordan Humphrey breaks a couple of tackles to get his second touchdown of the day.

videos.headline: Johnson's TD bring Tulane within one score
videos.description: Tulane quarterback Luke Skipper finds a wide-open Keenen Johnson for a 35-yard score.
